{
  "texts": [
    "In alignment with established best practices and previous SAA research 14, 16, 39, two licensed physicians assessed the appropriate triage level of each vignette independently.",
    "After rating all vignettes, the physicians discussed their answers in cases of disagreement to reach consensus on the appropriate triage level, thereby finalizing the solutions for this set.",
    "This approach guarantees that the triage levels assigned to each vignette are not only based on expert medical opinion but also on a harmonized understanding between the two assessing physicians 14, 16, 39.",
    "For the evaluation study, we compared data collected with our novel sampling approach to data collected with vignettes developed by Semigran et al.",
    "This dataset was selected for comparison, because it is openly accessible and has been used to evaluate the capabilities of both medical laypeople and SAAs."
  ]
}